01:23:18.456 --> 01:23:21.296
the short answer is the first approach is the better approach.

1407
01:23:21.636 --> 01:23:25.326
But depending on your specific use case, how much missing data there is,

1408
01:23:25.596 --> 01:23:28.386
how large your sample size is, and therefore how expensive

1409
01:23:28.456 --> 01:23:32.156
computationally doing the imputation is, you might have slightly

