1470
01:26:57.984 --> 01:27:00.344
If you see anything like that, don't believe it. It's a lie.

1471
01:27:00.644 --> 01:27:03.624
Nothing can save you if you have missing not at random missingness.

1472
01:27:05.104 --> 01:27:08.744
What it really comes down to is, is your data set rich enough

1473
01:27:09.064 --> 01:27:12.884
