1475
01:27:15.644 --> 01:27:19.524
So in cases where I think that we understand the missing

1476
01:27:19.604 --> 01:27:23.044
mechanism, I understand why it's missing, and we can potentially predict the

1477
01:27:23.084 --> 01:27:26.564
missing variable based on other information, then I don't get too worried.

1478
01:27:27.564 --> 01:27:31.424
It's the settings where... So to give an example, I was doing an analysis

1479
01:27:32.103 --> 01:27:35.864
