01:27:50.384 --> 01:27:54.364
no. That's really a big problem because that's a systematic

1485
01:27:54.404 --> 01:27:58.284
missingness that we can't predict from other things in the data." So

1486
01:27:59.164 --> 01:28:02.084
I'm always on the lookout for missing at random data, and really the only thing you

1487
01:28:02.104 --> 01:28:03.984
